smile.math.matrix

Class RowMajorMatrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • smile.math.matrix.RowMajorMatrix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DenseMatrix, Matrix, MatrixMultiplication<DenseMatrix,DenseMatrix>

    public class RowMajorMatrix
extends java.lang.Object
implements DenseMatrix
    A dense matrix whose data is stored in a single 1D array of doubles in row major order.
